I decided to order a nice Mother’s Day dinner for my family.  I called around 3pm with my order and scheduled a 6:30pm pickup time. I waited for over an hour and a half, was told multiple times my food was going to be ready in 20min. Finally at 8:15 I canceled my order. I understand we are in unique times, but their inability to the truth, and their lack of empathy was mind blowing. They had 25 people waiting and were still taking orders.  At what point do you realize you are ruining people’s Mother’s Day and stop taking orders. I don’t care how good the food is, I will never go back here.
